## Install in Stremio

Once the add-on is running and your hostname resolves, open this URL on your Android TV or any Stremio client:

```
https://YOUR-HOSTNAME/manifest.json
```

---

## Upgrade from a previous release

```bash
# Download to home directory
curl -L https://github.com/${REPO}/releases/download/${TAG}/stremio-addarr-install.tar.gz \
  -o ~/stremio-addarr-install.tar.gz

# Extract over existing installation (preserves your .env)
cd /opt/stremio-addarr
sudo tar -xzf ~/stremio-addarr-install.tar.gz --strip-components=1
sudo chown -R pi:pi /opt/stremio-addarr
npm ci --omit=dev
sudo systemctl restart stremio-addarr

# Verify
curl http://127.0.0.1:7010/healthz
```

